# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:77
msgid "Timing"
msgstr "Vremensko Podešavanje"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:78
msgid ""
"Changing how fast a clip plays is done with the :guilabel:`Time` property "
"and the :guilabel:`Timing` tool."
msgstr ""
"Promjena brzine reprodukcije isječka vrši se svojstvom :guilabel:`Time` i "
"alatom :guilabel:`Timing`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:80
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Time` menu offers presets such as normal, fast, slow, freeze, "
"and reverse. See details in :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Izbornik :guilabel:`Time` nudi unaprijed postavljene opcije poput normalno, "
"brzo, sporo, zamrzavanje i obrnuto. Pogledajte detalje u :ref:"
"`clip_time_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:81
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timing` tool lets you drag a clip’s edges to speed it up or "
"slow it down. OpenShot adds the needed Time keyframes and **scales your "
"other keyframes** so your animations stay aligned. Shorter clips play "
"faster, longer clips play slower. See more: :ref:`clip_time_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Alat :guilabel:`Timing` omogućuje vam povlačenje rubova isječka za "
"ubrzavanje ili usporavanje. OpenShot dodaje potrebne ključne okvire vremena "
"i **skalira vaše ostale ključne okvire** kako bi vaše animacije ostale "
"usklađene. Kraći isječci se reproduciraju brže, duži sporije. Više "
"informacija: :ref:`clip_time_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:86
msgid "Repeating"
msgstr "Ponavljanje"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:87
msgid ""
"To play a clip multiple times, use :guilabel:`Right-Click → Time → Repeat`."
msgstr ""
"Za višestruku reprodukciju isječka, koristite :guilabel:`Desni klik → "
"Vrijeme → Ponavljanje`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:89
msgid ":guilabel:`Loop` repeats in one direction (forward or reverse)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Loop` ponavlja u jednom smjeru (naprijed ili unatrag)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ping-Pong` alternates direction (forward then backward, etc.)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ping-Pong` izmjenjuje smjer (naprijed pa nazad, itd.)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom` can add a short pause between passes, speed up or slow "
"down each pass, including keyframes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Custom` može dodati kratku pauzu između prolaza, ubrzati ili "
"usporiti svaki prolaz, uključujući ključne okvire."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:93
msgid ""
"OpenShot writes the :guilabel:`Time` curve for you, and you can edit those "
"keyframes just like any other. See more: :ref:`clip_time_repeat_ref`."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot za vas piše :guilabel:`Time` krivulju, a te ključne okvire možete "
"uređivati kao i bilo koje druge. Više informacija: :ref:"
"`clip_time_repeat_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:97
msgid "Bézier Presets"
msgstr "Bézier unaprijed postavljene vrijednosti"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:98
msgid ""
"When using a Bézier curve for animation, OpenShot includes more than 20 "
"curve presets (which affect the shape of the curve). For example, **Ease-"
"In** has a more gradual slope at the beginning, making an animation move "
"slower at the beginning, and faster at the end. **Ease-In/Out (Back)** has a "
"gradual beginning and ending, but actually goes past the expected value and "
"then back (producing a bounce effect)."
msgstr ""
"Kada koristite Bézierovu krivulju za animaciju, OpenShot uključuje više od "
"20 unaprijed postavljenih krivulja (koje utječu na oblik krivulje). Na "
"primjer, **Ease-In** ima postupniji nagib na početku, što čini da animacija "
"sporije počinje, a brže završava. **Ease-In/Out (Back)** ima postupni "
"početak i kraj, ali zapravo prelazi očekivanu vrijednost i zatim se vraća "
"(stvarajući efekt odbijanja)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:103
msgid ""
"To choose a curve preset, right click on the small graph icon next to a key "
"frame."
msgstr ""
"Za odabir unaprijed postavljene krivulje, kliknite desnom tipkom miša na "
"malu ikonu grafikona pored ključnog okvira."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:110
msgid "Image Sequences"
msgstr "Sekvence slika"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you have a sequence of similarly named images (such as, cat001.png, "
"cat002.png, cat003.png, etc...), you can simply drag and drop one of them "
"into OpenShot, and you will be prompted to import the entire sequence. "
"OpenShot will playback these sequential images rapidly, as if they are "
"frames in a video. The rate or speed in which these images are displayed is "
"based on their frame rate."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate sekvencu slika sličnih imena (npr. cat001.png, cat002.png, cat003."
"png itd.), jednostavno povucite i ispustite jednu od njih u OpenShot, i bit "
"ćete upitani želite li uvesti cijelu sekvencu. OpenShot će brzo "
"reproducirati te slike jednu za drugom, kao da su okviri u videu. Brzina "
"prikaza ovih slika temelji se na njihovoj frekvenciji okvira."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:116
msgid ""
"**NOTE:** Be sure your image sequence starts at 0 or 1, or you will likely "
"receive an error when importing it into OpenShot. For example, if your "
"sequence starts at cat222.png, or has missing images in the sequence, "
"OpenShot will struggle to understand the sequence. An easy work-around is to "
"renumber the images so they start with 1."
msgstr ""
"**NAPOMENA:** Provjerite da vaša sekvenca slika počinje s 0 ili 1, inače "
"ćete vjerojatno dobiti pogrešku prilikom uvoza u OpenShot. Na primjer, ako "
"vaša sekvenca počinje s cat222.png ili ako nedostaju slike u sekvenci, "
"OpenShot će imati problema s razumijevanjem sekvence. Jednostavno rješenje "
"je preimenovati slike tako da počinju s 1."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:122
msgid ""
"To adjust the frame rate of the animation, right click and choose **File "
"Properties** in the **Project Files** panel, and adjust the frame rate. Once "
"you have set the correct frame rate, drag the animation onto the timeline."
msgstr ""
"Za podešavanje frekvencije okvira animacije, kliknite desnom tipkom i "
"odaberite **Svojstva datoteke** u panelu **Datoteke projekta**, te "
"prilagodite frekvenciju okvira. Nakon što postavite ispravnu frekvenciju "
"okvira, povucite animaciju na vremensku liniju."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:133
msgid "File Properties"
msgstr "Svojstva datoteke"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:133
msgid ""
"Select an image sequence in the **Project Files** panel, right click and "
"choose **File Properties**"
msgstr ""
"Odaberite sekvencu slika u panelu **Datoteke projekta**, kliknite desnom "
"tipkom i odaberite **Svojstva datoteke**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:134
msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "Frekvencija okvira"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:134
msgid ""
"Adjust the frame rate of the animation. Typically, hand-drawn animations use "
"12 frames per second."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite frekvenciju okvira animacije. Obično ručno crtane animacije "
"koriste 12 okvira u sekundi."
